      <Body><![CDATA[# Active Pipe Segment Model combing a compressor with a passive pipe segment

UNIT
pipe AS pipe_passive
compr AS recip_compressor_setF


EQUATION 
compr.Q = pipe.flow(0) ;
compr.P_disc = pipe.p(0) ;]]></Body>
